data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Custom Hydrangea with over 3200 Square Feet. This home offers 2 Owners Suites, Guest Room with access to the guest bathroom and a den/office/craft room. Lots of space  to entertain in this home with the open floor plan. Enjoy your private paradise with views of the 12th hole on Cranes Roost Golf Course. The kitchen has ample cabinet and counter space for your inner chef to create all your special meals. Space for eating and open to the family room. The split floor plan is great for company. 17 X 11 formal dining area with 12 foot ceilings is great for the whole family and friends when visiting. The main owners suite offers both a walk in shower and walk in tub. Huge walk in closet for all extra items. Owners suite also offers access to your private pool area. Laundry Room is located inside with extra storage. Two HVAC's and two Hot Waters tanks. The pool has a new pool pump. The front entrance is screen enclosed to give you and extra area to enjoy the outside. Plenty of parking for guest. This home is perfect for you and your guest without crowding your space. Plantation offers 2 golf courses, 3 swimming pools, restaurant, lounge with entertainment on the screened in back porch, walking trails, workout rooms, billiards, softball, pickle ball, gated entrances, 3 club houses, library and many activities. Low HOA. Plantation offers so much for you to do without the extra fees. All our amenities are included with your HOA fee except golf (join for a low fee or play when you want to) Storage is available for a small fee. Quick settlement.
